Specials
The Springs Club


Perth's biggest golfing secret... The Springs Club is a fun and challenging course, come play and see for yourself... you won't be disappointed.

Scroll down to find a tee time and price to suit. Prices are per person.

To maximise the enjoyment of your day and that of others:
- Please arrive at least 15 minutes prior to your booked tee-time.
- Please call the pro-shop for any adjustments or cancellations to existing bookings.
- Ensure you have a booking confirmation email - screenshots of tee-times are not valid bookings!
- Neat golf attire please - No singlets permitted.
- Enclosed footwear required.
- Directions of staff MUST be followed at all times.

- STRICTLY NO BYO ALCOHOL - golfers in possession of alcohol not purchased from The Springs Club will be removed from the facility immediately.
